        <head>THE STUPIDITY OF TRYING TO JAIL AN IDEA</head>
        <p>"I've served my time and what good has it done the state? Nothing has changed. My
            principles haven't. And the birth control movement is stronger than ever."-- <emph
                rend="italics">Statement by Margaret Sanger on her release from jail</emph></p>
